  "stem": "<p>In right triangle <math><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></math>, angle <math><mi>C</mi></math> is the right angle. The length of side <math><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math> is <math><mn>35</mn></math>, and the length of side <math><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math> is <math><mn>28</mn></math>. What is the value of <math><mi>cos</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>A</mi><mo>)</mo></math>?</p>",
